data.title: J.R. Smith, Basketball Player
data.meta_description: J.R. Smith stats and bio. Stats averages season by season. Quick access to game by game stats.
data.text:
J.R. Smith - Points

J.R. Smith scores a career high 60 points (2012)

On February 01, 2012, J.R. Smith set his career high in points in a China - CBA game. That day he scored 60 points in Zhejiang's home win against Qingdao, 122-110. He also had 8 rebounds, 2 assists, 6 steals. He shot 7/14 from two, 14/18 from three, shooting at 65.6% from the field. He also shot 4/5 from the free-throw line.

J.R. Smith - Rebounds

J.R. Smith grabs a career high 22 rebounds (2011)

On December 02, 2011, J.R. Smith set his career high in rebounds in a China - CBA game. That day he grabbed 22 rebounds in Zhejiang's home win against Bayi, 113-91. He also had 52 points, 4 assists, 7 steals.

J.R. Smith - Assists

J.R. Smith gives a career high 12 assists (2012)

On January 06, 2012, J.R. Smith set his career high in assists in a China - CBA game. That day he dished 12 assists in Zhejiang's home win against Xinjiang, 114-112. He also had 24 points, 9 rebounds, 3 steals.

J.R. Smith - Steals

J.R. Smith has a career high 7 steals (2011)

On December 02, 2011, J.R. Smith set his career high in steals in a China - CBA game. That day he reached 7 steals in Zhejiang's home win against Bayi, 113-91. He also had 52 points, 22 rebounds and 4 assists.

J.R. Smith - Blocks

J.R. Smith blocks a career high 4 shots (2015)

On November 28, 2015, J.R. Smith set his career high in blocks in a NBA game. That day he went for 4 blocks in Cleveland's home win against Brooklyn, 90-88. He also had 6 points, 5 rebounds and 1 assist.

J.R. Smith - Efficiency

J.R. Smith records a career high 66 efficiency rating (2011)

On December 02, 2011, J.R. Smith set his career high in efficiency in a China - CBA game. That day he accomplished 66 efficiency in Zhejiang's home win against Bayi, 113-91. He also had 52 points, 22 rebounds and 4 assists.
